text:
One of the biggest challenges for climate action today is Lack of information and poverty;
Most people are not so educated to the point where their major concern in life would be to know about their environment and climate changes, they are more concerned about feeding, shelter and jobs. 
But if this information could be resources and restructured in such a way that they smallest in the community would understand In the most easiest communicated way I believe it will become a norm and gradually such practices and action will be taken more seriously and intentionally.
